OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,FPolice are investigating a suspected
OL,7,F'racially motivated' arson attack at a
OL,8,Fformer gospel hall in West Belfast in
OL,9,Fthe early hours of Saturday morning.
OL,11,FThe Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,12,FService responded to the blaze on the
OL,13,FShankhill Road just after 2:45am.
OL,15,FPolice say it was determined that the
OL,16,Ffire had been caused by "deliberate
OL,17,Fignition" of the roof and has left the
OL,18,Fbuilding "totally gutted."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
