PN,44402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,FWhile the premicise was unused the
OL,7,FPSNI said it had recently been bought
OL,8,Fby "legitimate buisness owners" who
OL,9,Fwere aiming to bring jobs to the local
OL,10,Fcommunity.
OL,12,FThe police said, "As with any crime
OL,13,Fmotivated by hate, we will be
OL,14,Fproviding them with an enhanced level
OL,15,Fof supervision, investigation and
OL,16,Fsupport."
OL,26,@tD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
