FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,FSinn Fein MP Paul Maskey condemned the
OL,7,Falleged hate motivated arson attack
OL,8,Fsaid: "Targeting a building because of
OL,9,Fwho owns it is despicable, especially
OL,10,Fwhen areas are crying out for jobs and
OL,11,Finvestment.
OL,13,F"My thoughts are with the owners of
OL,14,Fthe building and all those affected by
OL,15,Fthis appalling incident."
OL,26,@nD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
