PN,44404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,FSDLP North Belfast Councillor Carl
OL,7,FWhyte also condemned the alleged arson
OL,8,Fattack saying: "This was devastating
OL,9,Ffor the owners of this business, who
OL,10,Fhave seen the roof completely
OL,11,Fdestroyed by fire and their
OL,12,Flivelihoods put at risk.
OL,14,F"When I visited this morning there
OL,15,Fwere bags of food still sitting in the
OL,16,Fdoorway, a reminder that these are
OL,17,Fordinary people trying to run a
OL,18,Fbusiness and support their families.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,F"This is not the first time this
OL,7,Fbusiness has been subjected to racist
OL,8,Fintimidation, and it is shameful that
OL,9,Fthe situation has escalated to this
OL,10,Fpoint. The owners and staff were
OL,11,Fproviding a service to the community
OL,12,Fand have much more to offer than those
OL,13,Fwho have targeted their business."
OL,15,FThe PSNI are asking anyone with CCTV
OL,16,Ffootage of the incident to come
OL,17,Fforward.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
