FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,FIn a statement Superintendent Finola
OL,7,FDornan said: "Just after 2.45am, we
OL,8,Freceived a report from our colleagues
OL,9,Fin Northern Ireland Fire & Rescue
OL,10,FService that they were attending a
OL,11,Ffire at an old Gospel Hall on the
OL,12,FShankill Road.
OL,14,F"On police arrival, Fire Service
OL,15,Fconfirmed that the fire had been
OL,16,Fcaused by deliberate ignition to the
OL,17,Froof. The building had been totally
OL,18,Fgutted by the blaze.
OL,26,@oD@NOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,F"Our detectives have begun carrying
OL,7,Fout enquiries and the community will
OL,8,Fsee a police presence in the area
OL,9,Ftoday."
OL,11,FSuperintendent Dornan continued: "This
OL,12,Fout-of-use building had been bought by
OL,13,Flegitimate business people who would
OL,14,Fhave brought jobs to the local
OL,15,Fcommunity and, as with any crime
OL,16,Fmotivated by hate, we will be
OL,17,Fproviding them with an enhanced level
OL,18,Fof supervision, investigation and
OL,19,Fsupport.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]sD@bOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,445,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,F"As a Police Service, we do not
OL,7,Funderestimate the impact hate-related
OL,8,Fcrimes have on victims, their families
OL,9,Fand wider communities. While we have a
OL,10,Fkey role to play in tackling,
OL,11,Fpreventing and supporting victims of
OL,12,Fhate incidents and hate crimes, this
OL,13,Fis a wider societal issue which cannot
OL,14,Fbe resolved by policing alone.
OL,16,F"We continue to work closely with our
OL,17,Fstatutory and voluntary partner
OL,18,Fagencies and the local community to
OL,19,Ffind solutions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
