PN,44409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F444A1780927877
OL,3,C'Racially motivated' arson suspected
OL,4,Cat former Belfast gospel hall
OL,6,F"We would encourage anyone with
OL,7,Finformation in relation to this arson
OL,8,Fattack to contact us on 101, quoting
OL,9,Freference 187 06/06/26. We would be
OL,10,Fparticularly keen to hear from anyone
OL,11,Fwith relevant CCTV, dashcam or other
OL,12,Ffootage."
